Package: secfacts
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: High-performance security evidence normalization & correlation engine
 secfacts is a specialized tool designed to combat security alert fatigue.
 It transforms raw findings from multiple scanners (SAST, DAST, SCA, Cloud)
 into actionable logical issues using a sharded actor correlation engine.
 .
 Key features:
  * Zero-copy streaming JSON/SARIF ingestion.
  * Deterministic lock-free deduplication.
  * Context-aware severity scoring.
  * CI/CD ready with configurable thresholds.
